.\" Laravel on Docker - LoD
.\" Marcin Szumski
.TH man 8 "08 Sep 2018" "1.0" "Laravel on Docker"
.SH NAME
LoD \- simply runs Laravel project on docker container
.SH SYNOPSIS
make [COMMAND]
.SH DESCRIPTION
This repository provides fast and easy way to run Laravel project using docker containers
.SH OPTIONS
.IP new
creates new laravel project. See Makefile if you want to change Laravel version
.IP start
starts docker container
.IP clean
removes www folder
.IP npm_install
runs "npm install" command
.IP npm_watch
runs "npm run watch" command
.IP composer_install
runs "composer install" command
.IP help
this screen
.SH BUGS
No known bugs.
.SH AUTHOR
Marcin Szumski (szumski.szumak@gmail.com)
